modules.description: This module processes TextMate grammars for syntax highlighting, supporting loading from PLIST or JSON structures into grammars and tokenizing source code lines into scope-annotated tokens. It handles data types like `plist`, `ezjsonm`, and `yojson` for grammar deserialization, and uses `grammar` and `stack` types to maintain tokenizer state across lines. Concrete use cases include parsing `.tmLanguage` files and incrementally tokenizing text buffers using a loaded grammar.
